               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184804030124"></xptr>
               <p>there of it—I went to the prisoner first—he said he had not got it—I found it in his pocket—he took it out, and gave it me—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I took it to pour my ale in; it was in my hand. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> You had no ale—it was in your pocket.</p>
